[{"catalog_class":"0100","catalog_id":"0010","catalog_type":"Required","catalog_checkbox":"&check;","catalog_checkbox_description":"","catalog_bin_loc":"","catalog_description":"Build (1st Generation) Branch","catalog_specs":"<p>Building a branch is the starting point. &nbsp;All options are applied to a branch.</p><br><br><ol><li>Configure Family Tree (Branch)</li><li>Configure Family Tree (Branch) Photo</li><li>Configure Family Tree (Branch) Descendants</li><li>Display Family Tree (Branch) Descendant Names</li><li>Data Entry: (Family Tree (Branch) Narrative</li><li>Configure <strong><i>Family Tree</i></strong> Link to Display: (Branch) Narrative in <strong><i>Isolated View</i></strong></li><li>Display Family Tree (Branch) Profile</li></ol>","catalog_price":"<p><span class='money-color'>$125.00</span> <strong><i>plus</i></strong> <span class='money-color'>$30.00</span> Set/Up Fee</p>","catalog_price_frequency":"<ul><li>Per (1st Generation) Branch</li><li>Set/Up fee applies only to 1st generation branches. &nbsp;All other generation branches (2nd, 3rd, and 4th) only pay branch charge.</li><li>Data Entry: (Family Tree (Branch) Narrative.<br><br>[Limit <strong><i>200</i></strong> Words] - Up to 3 revisions allowed before additional <span class='money-color'>$25.00</span> charge due.</li></ul>","catalog_active":"y"},{"catalog_class":"0100","catalog_id":"0020","catalog_type":"Option: 1","catalog_checkbox":"&check;","catalog_checkbox_description":"","catalog_bin_loc":"","catalog_description":"Activate Descendant (Pay Per Click)","catalog_specs":"<p>Choose this option, <u>if</u> you only want to see your descendant's profile information and <u>not</u> the names of their descendant children (even if they have them).</p><br><br><ol><li>Enable Descendant (Pay Per Click)</li><li>Display Descendant Profile on Click</li></ol>","catalog_price":"<p><span class='money-color'>$25.00</span></p>","catalog_price_frequency":"<ul><li>Per (Descendant) Click.</li><li>The Following fields Are Displayed:</li><ol><li>Descendant Photo</li><li>Computed Age</li><li>Year Born</li></ol><li>If Deceased?<br><br>An Asterisk (*) Indicating Deceased, Year Died, and Age at Death are also displayed</li></ul>","catalog_active":"y"},{"catalog_class":"0100","catalog_id":"0030","catalog_type":"Option: 2","catalog_checkbox":"&check;","catalog_checkbox_description":"","catalog_bin_loc":"","catalog_description":"Build (Descendant) Branch","catalog_specs":"<p>Choose this option, <u>if</u> you want to see your descendant's profile information <u>and</u> the names of their descendant children.</p><br><br><ol><li>Same Package Features as: <strong><i>0010 Build (1st Generation) Branch</i></strong></li><li>Except: A 2nd, 3rd, or 4th Generation (Branch) is built instead.</li></ol>","catalog_price":"<p><span class='money-color'>$125.00</span></p>","catalog_price_frequency":"<ul><li>Per (2nd, 3rd, or 4th Generational Branch)</li><li>Set/Up fee is not applicable to 2nd, 3rd, and 4th Generation Branches.</li><li>Data Entry: (Descendant) Branch Narrative.<br><br>[Limit <strong><i>200</i></strong> Words] - Up to 3 revisions allowed before additional <span class='money-color'>$25.00</span> charge due.</li></ul>","catalog_active":"y"},{"catalog_class":"0100","catalog_id":"0040","catalog_type":"Option: 3","catalog_checkbox":"&check;","catalog_checkbox_description":"","catalog_bin_loc":"","catalog_description":"Add Descendant (Narrative)","catalog_specs":"<p>Choose this option, <u>if</u> you want to write a narrative for your descendant (e.g. a tribute, a memorial, or to give praise).<br><br>This could be paired with Option 1 or Option 2</p><br><br><ol><li>Data Entry: (Descendant Narrative)</li><li>Display Descendant's Narrative when <strong><i>Family Tree</i></strong> Link is Clicked</li></ol>","catalog_price":"<p><span class='money-color'>$25.00</span></p>","catalog_price_frequency":"<ul><li>Per (Descendant) Narrative</li><li>Data Entry: (Descendant (Narrative).<br><br>[Limit <strong><i>200</i></strong> Words] - Up to 3 revisions allowed before additional <span class='money-color'>$25.00</span> charge due.</li></ul>","catalog_active":"y"},{"catalog_class":"0200","catalog_id":"0010","catalog_type":"","catalog_checkbox":"","catalog_checkbox_description":"","catalog_bin_loc":"","catalog_description":"Fantasy Photo","catalog_specs":"<p>Collaborate with <strong><i>Family Tree Creations</i></strong> to Design and Create:</p><br><ol><li>Fantasy Photos</li><li>Posters</li><li>Photo Collages</li><li>Remove Distracting Photo Backgrounds</li></ol>","catalog_price":"<p><span class='money-color'>$25.00</span>","catalog_price_frequency":"<ul><li>Per Image.</li><li>(Up to 3 revisions allowed before additional <span class='money-color'>$25.00</span> charge due).</li><li>We design your digital Image or poster and provide a JPEG file which you print yourself.</li></li></ul>","catalog_active":"y"},{"catalog_class":"0300","catalog_id":"0010","catalog_type":"","catalog_checkbox":"","catalog_checkbox_description":"","catalog_bin_loc":"","catalog_description":"Photo Plant Vase","catalog_specs":"<ol><li>Plant Vase (with 2024 Watkins Family Reunion Photo Decal).</li><li>A Memorable heirloom you'll want to pass down through generations!</li><li>5&frac12; inches tall</li></ol>","catalog_price":"<p><span class='money-color'>$15.00</span></p>","catalog_price_frequency":"<ul><li>Per Vase.</li><li>Limited Time Offer, Buy 2, Get One Free!</li><li>Potting Soil and Plant (Not Included).</li></ul>","catalog_active":"y"},{"catalog_class":"0300","catalog_id":"0020","catalog_type":"","catalog_checkbox":"","catalog_checkbox_description":"","catalog_bin_loc":"","catalog_description":"Photo Plant Vase","catalog_specs":"<ol><li>Plant Vase (with 2024 Watkins Family Reunion Photo Decal).</li><li>A Memorable heirloom you'll want to pass down through generations!</li><li>5&frac12; inches tall</li></ol>","catalog_price":"<p><span class='money-color'>$15.00</span></p>","catalog_price_frequency"